<div class="title">A Lovely Drug</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I, Cannabis & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Kid+-+B&Exact=1">Kid - B</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Kid - B. "A Lovely Drug: An Experience with 2C-I, Cannabis & Alcohol (exp49237)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 17, 2007. erowid.org/exp/49237</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

